STEPS TO RENAME FILES
I used this command to rename my files, for i in {1..6}; do
  mv "Day$i" "Task$i"
done


How it works:

for i in {1..6}; do → loops i from 1 to 6

mv "Day$i" "Task$i" → renames Day1 → Task1, Day2 → Task2, etc.

done → ends the loop

I used the command, ls to confirm if the files were successfully renamed
